{"tid":2282671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Google Photos 宣佈 2021 年 6 月停止免費無限儲存","createTime":"2020-11-12T04:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T12:01:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"93b4c5dd47e2af0336aae65eddf98a3389b662be","tid":2282671,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:21:05.000Z","msg":"長久以來 Google Photos 也是 iPhone、Android 用戶備份照片、影片的好幫手，自從 Google Photos 推出「無限」免費備份「高質」照片、影片後，很多人已習慣用它每天為手機的照片備份。特别是 iOS 用戶，預設使用 HEIC 格式，Google Photos 是原相上載備份，不會再壓縮，因為將 HEIC 壓縮反而會令照片檔案容量增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，這美好的免費日子終於要結束，Google Photos 宣佈將於 2021 年 6 月 1 日開始，Google Photos 會將「新」上載的照片、影片將會視為文件般計算，如果總容量超過 15GB 將會要求用戶付費升級 Google One 儲存容量。而在 2021 年 6 月 1 日之前已上載的照片／影片可獲豁免計算儲存空間。此外，如果用戶的帳號 2 年也沒有登入，儲存的資料將會被清除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/11/12/google-photos-stop-free-unlimited-storage/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F11%2F12%2Fgoogle-photos-stop-free-unlimited-storage%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=d58cb5f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/11/12/google-photos-stop-free-unlimited-storage/</a>"},{"pid":"d3822299b49f9a1708163dd771fb6366f57697a9","tid":2282671,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5424c640376a01d6a5d47bf8cb4fb95f4b54a97f","tid":2282671,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea2796